comments: Juzang (UTA) briefly grasps Green's (HOU) jersey but does not affect his FOM as he goes to set the pick on the perimeter.
Green (HOU) establishes himself in Dunn's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Dunn (UTA) swipes down and initiates contact to Green's (HOU) lower body that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Thompson (HOU) and Collins (UTA) briefly engage and disengage as they attempt to establish position in the lane.
Dunn (UTA) establishes himself in Smith Jr.'s (HOU) path and the two players move along the same path towards the basket as they engage.
Brooks (HOU) legally contests Hendricks' (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Juzang (UTA) applies a hand to Green's (HOU) front, affecting his SQBR.
Smith Jr. (HOU) contests the driving shot attempt and incidental "high-five" contact occurs with Dunn (UTA) after the release.
Collins (UTA) establishes himself in Thompson's (HOU) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Smith Jr. (HOU) legally contests Juzang's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Green (HOU) legally contests Juzang's (UTA) layup attempt.
Juzang (UTA) reaches in towards the ball when VanVleet (HOU) receives the throw-in and the ensuing contact is marginal.
Dunn (UTA) commits a take foul on Green (HOU).
